cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a regularization technique for high-dimensional small-sample problems, which is a common issue in machine learning and data analysis. The proposed method is demonstrated on logistic regression for face image and brain image classification, indicating that it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
